-- ft.h0: Install `fpm`

`fpm` is available as a crate, you can install it using:


-- ft.code:
lang: sh

cargo install fpm


-- ft.h1: Upgrade `fpm`

As of Rust 1.41.0, `cargo install` does an auto upgrade of a package if it is 
already installed. 

If you are using older Rust, then run the following to upgrade.


-- ft.code:
lang: sh

cargo install --force fpm